# 11. Notes for publication-level analysis

## 11.1 Database and software versions

    # Recommended version recording commands
    porechop_abi --version
    NanoPlot --version
    chopper --version
    seqkit version
    kraken2 --version
    abricate --version
    flye --version
    minimap2 --version
